      - status: stable
        content:
          name: cdm/base/staticdata/identifier/AssignedIdentifier
          description: A class to specify the identifier value and its associated version.
          identifier:
            description: The identifier value.
            type:
              blueId: F5GfdsSNcjLAm9anbfMQqxdxAFonErhU5UXFbQzq1zXY
            schema:
              required:
                type:
                  blueId: 4EzhSubEimSQD3zrYHRtobfPPWntUuhEz8YcdxHsi12u
                value: true
          version:
            description: |
              The identifier version, which is specified as an integer and is meant to be incremented each time the transaction terms (whether contract or event) change. This version is made option to support the use case where the identifier is referenced without the version. The constraint that a contract and a lifecycle event need to have an associated version is enforced through data rules.
            type:
              blueId: 5WNMiV9Knz63B4dVY5JtMyh3FB4FSGqv7ceScvuapdE1
        versions:
          - repositoryVersionIndex: 0
            typeBlueId: CNZP6GsTZi731ekV62fUVAXc2yL9DVbiHje2LSX8DmWf
            attributesAdded: []
      - status: stable
        content:
          name: cdm/base/staticdata/identifier/CommodityLocationIdentifierTypeEnum
          description: Defines the enumerated values to specify the nature of a location identifier.
          type:
            blueId: DLRQwz7MQeCrzjy9bohPNwtCxKEBbKaMK65KBrwjfG6K
          schema:
