      - status: stable
        content:
          name: cdm/product/asset/CashflowRepresentation
          description: |
            A data defining:  the cashflow representation of a swap trade.
          cashflowsMatchParameters:
            description: |
              A true/false flag to indicate whether the cashflows match the parametric definition of the stream, i.e. whether the cashflows could be regenerated from the parameters without loss of information.
            type:
              blueId: 4EzhSubEimSQD3zrYHRtobfPPWntUuhEz8YcdxHsi12u
            schema:
              required:
                type:
                  blueId: 4EzhSubEimSQD3zrYHRtobfPPWntUuhEz8YcdxHsi12u
                value: true
          paymentCalculationPeriod:
            description: |
              The adjusted payment date and associated calculation period parameters required to calculate the actual or projected payment amount. A list of payment calculation period elements may be ordered in the document by ascending adjusted payment date. An FpML document containing an unordered list of payment calculation periods is still regarded as a conformant document.
            type:
              blueId: 6aehfNAxHLC1PHHoDr3tYtFH3RWNbiWdFancJ1bypXEY
            itemType:
              blueId: 5X3D2ENebv1d9zFVGd1EdB4mT992xV4BvQ4xjuwktuNK
            schema:
              minItems:
                type:
                  blueId: 5WNMiV9Knz63B4dVY5JtMyh3FB4FSGqv7ceScvuapdE1
                value: 0
        versions:
          - repositoryVersionIndex: 0
            typeBlueId: FG2jLxQvPs3SKvJ3Jmg6mN7bHSMMac1ZBTWtVvnHP8M7
            attributesAdded: []
      - status: stable
        content:
          name: cdm/product/asset/CommodityPayout
          description: |
            Payout based on the averaged price of a referenced underlier. (e.g. Commodities). Can represent both average (average of many) & bullet (average of 1) pricing
          averagingFeature:
            description: Indicates if the averaging calculation, when applicable, is weighted or unweighted.
            type:
              blueId: DgMT9GvGPfVpoxATLX7UH2QtPrCD7csg3P5rdgiQxAUg
          calculationPeriodDates:
            description: Defines the calculation period dates schedule.
            type:
              blueId: HNqe2eLHMNHdTJAqM3zJLo9SBP9LgZu1vfSbhQ9KX51v
          commodityPriceReturnTerms:
            description: Defines parameters in which the commodity price is assessed.
            type:
              blueId: 5x1sDH43jpfnxCpn7SxGocGurJQPFSuhA9VqKTEj3p4y
          delivery:
            description: Contains the information relative to the delivery of the asset.
            type:
              blueId: DFCwxwyJL859yeqbrr3oY7vncLWeadysD9VJGA6LGJgK
          fxFeature:
            description: Defines quanto or composite FX features that are included in the swap leg.
            type:
              blueId: 4vFVJ5RzFY4D7trKTFXSjcQJv9vQk2V1fzpSsA4MHF3u
          payerReceiver:
            description: Canonical representation of the payer and receiver parties applicable to each payout leg.
            type:
              blueId: Cx2eHN58eqWKXnZwn6JDYBzAfG95QSEAWjQhbX1R5An3
          paymentDates:
            description: |
              Defines the payment date schedule, as defined by the parameters that are needed to specify it, either in a parametric way or by reference to another schedule of dates (e.g. the valuation dates).
            type:
              blueId: 913TgdFLeMHEAXnndV1KuUqmoxUtRjXn8X8JRX4n632b
            schema:
              required:
                type:
                  blueId: 4EzhSubEimSQD3zrYHRtobfPPWntUuhEz8YcdxHsi12u
                value: true
          priceQuantity:
            description: |
              Each payout leg must implement the quantity concept as a 'resolvable' type, which allows for different payout legs to be linked to each other (e.g. in the case of cross-curreny products).
            type:
              blueId: F4ihqR7D44ZpGGutb98mpsdE6QNtkrVZM4oiK6Vuzcsy
          pricingDates:
            description: Specifies specific dates or parametric rules for the dates on which the price will be determined.
            type:
              blueId: ENR8ZMb3BXhAA9nevcEyKgFFFrZ2fgr7kuxCniYTsx1w
            schema:
              required:
                type:
                  blueId: 4EzhSubEimSQD3zrYHRtobfPPWntUuhEz8YcdxHsi12u
                value: true
          principalPayment:
            description: |
              The specification of the principal exchange. Optional as only applicable in the case of cross-currency or zero-coupon swaps with a final payment.
            type:
              blueId: 79fSZCgPXnnm5bsD9s4XCQXn5MaCb8UAVq6ybHFbLdpq
          schedule:
            description: |
              Allows the full representation of a payout by defining a set of schedule periods. It supports standard schedule customization by expressing all the dates, quantities, and pricing data in a non-parametric way.
            type:
              blueId: 4W1R4RHyg7dDwmQXUBPtdq2118vcYaxmhXXpAsyJ45iG
          settlementTerms:
            description: |
              Each payout leg must specifies its settlement terms, including the delivery type (i.e. cash vs physical, and their respective terms), the transfer type (DvP etc.) and settlement date, if any.
            type:
              blueId: 7zkmbj4175pTZ3exYCBnCyVdiSaAT2SEfkxhDTus8iLY
          underlier:
            description: |
              Identifies the underlying product that is referenced for pricing of the applicable leg in a swap. Referenced in the '2018 ISDA CDM Equity Confirmation for Security Equity Swap' as Security.
            type:
              blueId: this#5
            schema:
              required:
                type:
                  blueId: 4EzhSubEimSQD3zrYHRtobfPPWntUuhEz8YcdxHsi12u
                value: true
